      <para styleclass="Heading1">Build Events</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-style:normal;">On the Build Events property page you can specify command lines that need to be run before or after the build process.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-style:normal;">You can use this for example to run a tool that generates source code or to copy the output DLLs to another folder.</text></para>
